  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/57cad692b91e97315625f320c8f1f21f.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/57cad692b91e97315625f320c8f1f21f.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/57cad692b91e97315625f320c8f1f21f.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"As the legends say there is a hidden Mask in the <strong>PhaRaBis</strong> pyramid left by the God of Sun. The mask which makes the user control the elements of the nature could only be used by Pharaohs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But the last pharaoh put this Mask in a really hidden room. For centuries, people that enter the pyramid to find that secret room have been lost. It is said that the room is cursed and who dares to enter will never be out.\"</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RUN FOR YOUR LIFE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/b95d9c7800b262cd0326e541fc80a807.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/b95d9c7800b262cd0326e541fc80a807.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/b95d9c7800b262cd0326e541fc80a807.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape the relentless Guardian of the PhaRaBis Pyramid, a terrifying creature that hunts you through every dark corner.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNCOVER THE SECRETS!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/567ac54d93192923f1f30122eb7cf971.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/567ac54d93192923f1f30122eb7cf971.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/567ac54d93192923f1f30122eb7cf971.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the pyramid’s ancient mysteries and unlock the power of the legendary mask.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT TO SURVIVE!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/97ae1409d1e7d0aa65f921fa8c8dfc4e.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/97ae1409d1e7d0aa65f921fa8c8dfc4e.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/97ae1409d1e7d0aa65f921fa8c8dfc4e.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle terrifying mummies that guard the pyramid’s secrets and fight to stay alive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DANGER AROUND EVERY CORNER!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/4ebe40b559c24c30afb146c4f31ea1e7.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/4ebe40b559c24c30afb146c4f31ea1e7.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/4ebe40b559c24c30afb146c4f31ea1e7.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The PhaRaBis Pyramid is filled with traps—one wrong move, and it could be your last.<br><br><br>-------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally released in 2017 and beloved by horror fans on mobile platforms, this game has finally arrived on PC due to overwhelming demand! Dive into the mysterious and terrifying world of the PhaRaBis Pyramid and embark on an exciting adventure to uncover the secrets of the mask!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/57cad692b91e97315625f320c8f1f21f.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/57cad692b91e97315625f320c8f1f21f.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/57cad692b91e97315625f320c8f1f21f.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"As the legends say there is a hidden Mask in the <strong>PhaRaBis</strong> pyramid left by the God of Sun. The mask which makes the user control the elements of the nature could only be used by Pharaohs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But the last pharaoh put this Mask in a really hidden room. For centuries, people that enter the pyramid to find that secret room have been lost. It is said that the room is cursed and who dares to enter will never be out.\"</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RUN FOR YOUR LIFE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/b95d9c7800b262cd0326e541fc80a807.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/b95d9c7800b262cd0326e541fc80a807.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/b95d9c7800b262cd0326e541fc80a807.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape the relentless Guardian of the PhaRaBis Pyramid, a terrifying creature that hunts you through every dark corner.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNCOVER THE SECRETS!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/567ac54d93192923f1f30122eb7cf971.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/567ac54d93192923f1f30122eb7cf971.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/567ac54d93192923f1f30122eb7cf971.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the pyramid’s ancient mysteries and unlock the power of the legendary mask.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT TO SURVIVE!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/97ae1409d1e7d0aa65f921fa8c8dfc4e.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/97ae1409d1e7d0aa65f921fa8c8dfc4e.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/97ae1409d1e7d0aa65f921fa8c8dfc4e.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle terrifying mummies that guard the pyramid’s secrets and fight to stay alive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DANGER AROUND EVERY CORNER!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/4ebe40b559c24c30afb146c4f31ea1e7.poster.avif?t=1745837580\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/4ebe40b559c24c30afb146c4f31ea1e7.webm?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3650550/extras/4ebe40b559c24c30afb146c4f31ea1e7.mp4?t=1745837580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The PhaRaBis Pyramid is filled with traps—one wrong move, and it could be your last.<br><br><br>-------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally released in 2017 and beloved by horror fans on mobile platforms, this game has finally arrived on PC due to overwhelming demand! Dive into the mysterious and terrifying world of the PhaRaBis Pyramid and embark on an exciting adventure to uncover the secrets of the mask!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
